properties.description: Copy all Excel files in the "Finance - Standard Costs" and Spread folder on SharePoint to the "standard-costs-files" container. Then copy the production files to [RAW].[F.Production_StanlowBDR] and [RAW].[F.Production_StanlowPTP]. Then copies the previous month stock file (if it exists) to the [RAW].[F.ActTankItem]  table.
